com.google.publicalerts.cap.edxl.types

Class ValueList

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.publicalerts.cap.edxl.types.ValueList

  • public class ValueList
extends java.lang.Object
    Generic bean to hold XML parsed entries of the form:

    valueListUrn value

    where the content of is the Uniform Resource Name of a published list of values and definitions, and the content of is a string (which may represent a number) denoting the value itself. Multiple instances of the may occur with a single within the container.
